<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST95/Beltway.ST1995.html 204.71.237.92 19970114183138 text/html 7500
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 18:31:54 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:18:46 GMT
Content-length: 7316
Content-type: text/html
