http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST95/WPPSS1.ST1995.html 204.71.237.92 19970114183416 text/html 7040
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 18:34:27 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:20:17 GMT
