http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST95/ESA2.ST1995.html 204.71.237.92 19970114184027 text/html 7265
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 18:40:17 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:19:09 GMT
