http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST94/Gun94.html 204.71.237.92 19970114184537 text/html 6345
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 18:46:01 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:17:15 GMT
