http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST93/Markets93.html 204.71.237.92 19970114185854 text/html 6421
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 18:58:54 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:13:05 GMT
