http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST93/LearnCurv93.html 204.71.237.92 19970114190404 text/html 6866
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 19:04:17 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:13:01 GMT
Content-length: 6682
Content-type: text/html
