http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST92/NewShade92.html 204.71.237.92 19970114190837 text/html 7334
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 19:08:42 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:09:26 GMT
Content-length: 7150
