<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/nationalreview/29july96/week.html 204.71.237.92 19970114193952 text/html 16398
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 19:40:13 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 19-Jul-96 15:29:36 GMT
