http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/nationalreview/11dec95/week.htm 204.71.237.92 19970114201519 text/html 12074
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 20:15:36 GMT
