http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/nationalreview/25sep95/litengin.htm 204.71.237.92 19970114202716 text/html 9402
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 20:27:31 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Dec-95 21:09:47 GMT
Content-length: 9218
